WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
FLORIDA TO BAHAMAS.
DISTRESS SIGNAL RECEIVED ON 406 MHZ FROM 38 FOOT S/V LEGACY,
WHITE HULL, ONE PERSON ON BOARD, BETWEEN MIAMI (25-46N 080-13W)
AND BIMINI (25-44N 079-15W). VESSELS IN VICINITY
REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
REPORTS TO U.S. COAST GUARD MIAMI, PHONE: 305 415 6800,
E-MAIL:RCCMIAMI@USCG.MIL.
